{"tid":1800031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先放工見到對學生妹","createTime":"2019-12-27T12:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-27T14:02:19.000Z","uid":58316,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"29a9c7819cceff5d6d2e2d003f56b13b8ed58406","tid":1800031,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:08:50.000Z","msg":"放左工第一時間整返杯廢水<br />\n咁買左等嗌飛<br />\n隔籬補習社啱啱放學<br />\n咁行過另一檔<br />\n順便買d燒賣魚蛋<br />\n咁有對學生妹<br />\n拎住d補習notes<br />\n爭論緊食邊檔<br />\n兩檔痴住打對頭<br />\n其中一檔有雞蛋仔<br />\n但另一檔又有串燒<br />\n其中一個學生妹明顯高質好多<br />\n似陳自瑤mix陳瀅<br />\n仲要好白<br />\n係有少少唇毛<br />\n另一個就黑黑地咁<br />\n一路望住正個個<br />\n一路等阿姐燒雞軟骨雞腎<br />\n但睇得出唔靚個個其實知個個望靚個個<br />\n冇人望自己<br />\n其實d女係知<br />\n永遠記得佢個表情"},{"pid":"e9d7825ad58e8c404cc6894be6be4547733238da","tid":1800031,"uid":71508,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:14:37.000Z","msg":"女人係奸<br />\n特登同d唔靚做朋友<br />\n突顯自己<br />\n例如<br />\n靚女身邊總有肥婆friend"},{"pid":"e7c42318870de5f881e7824d1a4ffdb38c0a51dd","tid":1800031,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"圖都無張"},{"pid":"12f99d624952d22a366fc5283bdaabc33f0bd9b6","tid":1800031,"uid":243756,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T12:21:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XMR4mWL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXMR4mWL.gif&h=d674993e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c16dddf590d7b561c2d31d279343d940bc6395e4","tid":1800031,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-27T14:02:19.000Z","msg":"睇錯有陰唇毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}